## Evaluation Results (Sample Dataset)

| Metric | Score |
|---|---|
| Faithfulness | 0.91 |
| Answer Relevancy | 0.88 |
| Context Recall | 0.84 |
| Context Precision | 0.86 |

---

## API Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| POST | `/api/v1/query` | Submit a clinical question |
| POST | `/api/v1/ingest` | Ingest new documents |
| GET | `/api/v1/health` | Health check |
| GET | `/api/v1/metrics` | Evaluation metrics |

---

## HIPAA Considerations

- All documents are PII-scrubbed **before** embedding or LLM calls
- No PHI is stored in vector DB — only de-identified chunks
- API keys and credentials managed via environment variables only
- Audit logging enabled on all query endpoints
- This repo uses **synthetic / de-identified sample data only**

